Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,================== EDCN ==================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在这烟波浩翰的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:48.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}万千世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:52.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你我二人是否相遇？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:03.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}虽然不会轻易相信命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:06.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只是希望你我能同见一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:16.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论明天迎来的是泪眼还是欢颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:21.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}都不合适后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:28.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只因为有你陪伴在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:35.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所以我才能坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:40.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也许是徒绕远路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:44.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就是绕远路又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:55.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}路依旧延绵不尽
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,================== EDJP ==================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}色とりどりの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:48.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界で偶然に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:52.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}出会ってしまったの？　二人は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:03.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}運命なんて簡単に信じれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:06.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}おんなじ夢　見ていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:16.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}泣き顔も笑顔も　やって来る明日に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:21.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}後悔に似合わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:28.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君がそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:35.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}強い気持ちでいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:40.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ジグザグかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:44.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ジグザグでもいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:49.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fsp0}forever and ever with you
